OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fshowers continuing overnight with some
OL,7,Fclearer spells in between. Showers
OL,8,Fperhaps becoming more organised and
OL,9,Fheavier later in the night with a
OL,10,Fstronger breeze.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,13,Ffurther spells of showery rain,
OL,14,Fpossibly heavy at times. A band of
OL,15,Fmore persistent rain and stronger
OL,16,Fwinds then arriving later in the
OL,17,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
